Additional Notices (informational, not part of the MIT license terms):

This repository's PowerShell scripts download AMD installer EXEs at runtime
from amd.com. The scripts do NOT redistribute AMD's binaries, INF files, or
catalog files. AMD's End User License Agreement (EULA) for the chipset and
graphics installer packages applies independently to those files; users are
responsible for reviewing and complying with AMD's terms.

The scripts also generate a self-signed code-signing certificate and re-sign
AMD's INF / .cat files using that certificate. By doing so, the user becomes
the cryptographic publisher of those drivers from the operating system's
perspective. WHQL certification (Microsoft Hardware Lab Kit) is invalidated
on any driver this pipeline replaces.

This software is intended for personal, lab, and verification use only. It is
not appropriate for production deployment at scale, and the contributors
provide no warranty, support, or fitness-for-purpose guarantee.
